{"tid":2224323,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鋪路健康碼 內地港人入境擬免14日隔離","createTime":"2020-09-30T12:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T12:08:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"36c5ab55ac017445266f2cccaa913b67129c30bd","tid":2224323,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:06:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/NX5ZKGUARZFCTBI6UEOTYLAYOI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2FNX5ZKGUARZFCTBI6UEOTYLAYOI%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kylYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=72cc6b14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2FNX5ZKGUARZFCTBI6UEOTYLAYOI%2F&h=17faaa3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/NX5ZKGUARZFCTBI6UEOTYLAYOI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n鋪路健康碼 內地港人入境擬免14日隔離<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】在建制派搖旗吶喊下，特首林鄭月娥昨形容內地疫情「受控得咁好」，正積極計劃容許居住內地的港人只需持有核酸檢測陰性證明，回港後可豁免14日強制隔離，並預告內地健康碼已進入最後研究階段。有立法會議員斥此舉恐重蹈覆轍，引發第四波疫情，促政府取消豁免隔離制度。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：疫情緩和餐廳逼爆政府急修例  逾四人一枱 告埋食客<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥昨表示，港府正積極跟進與內地及澳門等往來的14日強制檢疫措施，指當局正考慮先讓居住或身處內地的港人，成為首批。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n政府昨又宣佈，考慮把內地及澳門列入疫情持續受控或感染數字低水平的「第二類指明地區」，並修訂法例599C章及599E章，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cRtXtiogU9dAnT2obqQaBYrQYJk=/1766x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3AYJLKQIMNEDNOVKMW26RMLLVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcRtXtiogU9dAnT2obqQaBYrQYJk%3D%2F1766x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3AYJLKQIMNEDNOVKMW26RMLLVU.jpg&h=8d528fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■專家指容許內地港人返港後不需強制隔離會帶來風險。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n議員斥靠害 恐爆第四波<br />\n<br />\n不過，根據日本厚生勞動省資料，日本8及9月在當地機場發現最少17名來自中國的旅客檢測到武肺病毒，全部沒有病徵，顯示內地並非完全沒有隱形患者的風險。<br />\n<br />\n呼吸系統專科醫生梁子超表示，容許內地港人返港後不需強制隔離會帶來風險，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員郭家麒反對由內地返港的港人可獲豁免隔離，「我唔反對縮短佢哋嘅隔離時間，。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"f87d3bf21bee7d79d240a5cc68d6f06e46e19b76","tid":2224323,"uid":111425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:07:28.000Z","msg":"第四波準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5991ccd5572e82d4774fa9637ba61a938eb443","tid":2224323,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f87d3bf21bee7d79d240a5cc68d6f06e46e19b76","tid":2224323,"uid":111425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:07:28.000Z","msg":"第四波準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:08:19.000Z","msg":"WFH<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}